ist-group review-rating"> <div>Story <span class="p-l-md pull-right">10</span></div> <div>Acting/Cast <span class="p-l-md pull-right">10</span></div> <div>Music <span class="p-l-md pull-right">9.5</span></div> <div>Rewatch Value <span class="p-l-md pull-right">10</span></div> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="review-spoiler">This review may contain spoilers</div>   <p><strong>First Impression</strong></p>  This show is going to be FANTASTIC. I already knew this show was going to be great just from watching the trailer but, so far for this being the first episode....this show is unbelievably amazing. The concept alone is amazing...not to mention the cinematography is absolutely stunning along with the plot and cast. I can just tell this show is going to be a rewatch for me once it's finished.<br><br><br>Alongside the NC scene...it is an absolute masterpiece already. The side-couple....yeah, you heard me THE SIDE-COUPLES NC scene is so fantastic and intense that I'm sitting on the edge of my seat waiting for the next episode on Friday  <p class="read-more"><a href="#" class="button">Read More</a></p>  <div class="review-helpful m-t p-t xb-t"> <div class="review-vote review-helpful-378183"><span class="text-muted">Was this review helpful to you?</span> <button class="btn btn-xs white helpful review-cast-helpful" data-id="378183" data-label="Yes"><span>Yes</span></button> <button class="btn btn-xs white unhelpful review-cast-helpful" data-id="378183" data-label="No"><span>No</span></button> <button class="btn btn-xs white review-cancel-vote" data-id="378183"><span>Cancel</span></button>  <button class="btn btn-xs btn-gift-award" data-id="378183"></button>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>
